[{"id": 560004, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5178, "text": "G\u00f6klerde ve yerde olanlar\u0131n t\u00fcm\u00fc, Melik; Kudd\u00fcs; Aziz; Hakim olan Allah'\u0131 tesbih eder."}, {"id": 560005, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5179, "text": "O, \u00fcmm\u00eeler i\u00e7inde, kendilerinden olan ve onlara ayetlerini okuyan, onlar\u0131 ar\u0131nd\u0131r\u0131p-temizleyen ve onlara kitap ve hikmeti \u00f6\u011freten bir el\u00e7i g\u00f6nderendir. Oysa onlar, bundan \u00f6nce ger\u00e7ekten a\u00e7\u0131k\u00e7a bir sap\u0131kl\u0131k i\u00e7inde idiler."}, {"id": 560006, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5180, "text": "Ve hen\u00fcz kendilerine ula\u015f\u0131p-kat\u0131lmam\u0131\u015f olan di\u011ferlerine de (peygamber g\u00f6nderilmi\u015ftir); O (Allah), \u00fcst\u00fcn ve g\u00fc\u00e7l\u00fcd\u00fcr, h\u00fck\u00fcm ve hikmet sahibidir."}, {"id": 560007, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5181, "text": "Bu, Allah'\u0131n diledi\u011fine verdi\u011fi fazl (l\u00fctuf ve ihsan)\u0131d\u0131r. Allah, b\u00fcy\u00fck fazl sahibidir."}, {"id": 560008, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5182, "text": "Kendilerine Tevrat y\u00fckletilip de sonra onu (i\u00e7indeki derin anlamlar\u0131, hikmet ve h\u00fck\u00fcmleriyle gere\u011fi gibi) y\u00fcklenmemi\u015f olanlar\u0131n durumu, koskoca kitap y\u00fck\u00fc ta\u015f\u0131yan e\u015fe\u011fin durumu gibidir. Allah'\u0131n ayetlerini yalanlayan kavmin durumu ne k\u00f6t\u00fcd\u00fcr. Allah, zalim bir kavmi hidayete erdirmez."}, {"id": 560009, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5183, "text": "De ki: \"Ey Yahudi olanlar, e\u011fer siz, (b\u00fct\u00fcn) insanlardan ayr\u0131 olarak yaln\u0131zca sizlerin ger\u00e7ekten Allah'\u0131n velileri (dost ve sevgili kullar\u0131) oldu\u011funuzu \u00f6ne s\u00fcr\u00fcyorsan\u0131z, \u015fu halde \u00f6l\u00fcm\u00fc temenni edin; e\u011fer do\u011fru s\u00f6zl\u00fc iseniz (bunu \u00e7ekinmeden yap\u0131n).\""}, {"id": 560010, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5184, "text": "Oysa onlar, ellerinin \u00f6ne takdim ettikleri dolay\u0131s\u0131yla bunu hi\u00e7bir zaman temenni edemezler. Allah, zalimleri bilendir."}, {"id": 560011, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 553, "ruku": 486, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5185, "text": "De ki: \"Elbette sizin kendisinden ka\u00e7t\u0131\u011f\u0131n\u0131z \u00f6l\u00fcm, \u015f\u00fcphesiz sizinle kar\u015f\u0131la\u015f\u0131p-bulu\u015facakt\u0131r. Sonra gayb\u0131 da, m\u00fc\u015fahede edilebileni de bilen (Allah)a d\u00f6nd\u00fcr\u00fcleceksiniz; O da size yapt\u0131klar\u0131n\u0131z\u0131 haber verecektir.\""}, {"id": 560012, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 554, "ruku": 487, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5186, "text": "Ey iman edenler, cuma g\u00fcn\u00fc namaz i\u00e7in \u00e7a\u011fr\u0131 yap\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 zaman, hemen Allah'\u0131 zikretmeye ko\u015fun ve al\u0131\u015f-veri\u015fi b\u0131rak\u0131n. E\u011fer bilirseniz, bu sizin i\u00e7in daha hay\u0131rl\u0131d\u0131r."}, {"id": 560013, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 554, "ruku": 487, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5187, "text": "Art\u0131k namaz\u0131 k\u0131l\u0131nca, yery\u00fcz\u00fcnde da\u011f\u0131l\u0131n. Allah'\u0131n fazl\u0131n\u0131 isteyip-aray\u0131n ve Allah'\u0131 \u00e7ok\u00e7a zikredin; umulur ki felaha (kurtulu\u015fa ve umduklar\u0131n\u0131za) kavu\u015fmu\u015f olursunuz."}, {"id": 560014, "identifier": "tr.bulac", "surah_number": 62, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u062c\u0645\u0639\u0629", "surah_en_name": "Al-Jumu'a", "surah_en_name_translation": "Friday", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 554, "ruku": 487, "hizb_quarter": 221, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "tr", "name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "transelator_en_name": "Al\u0130 Bula\u00e7", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5188, "text": "Oysa onlar (kendilerini t\u00fcm\u00fcyle Allah'a ve \u0130slam'a teslim etmeyenler) bir ticaret ya da bir e\u011flence g\u00f6rd\u00fckleri zaman, (hemen) ona s\u00f6k\u00fcn ettiler ve seni ayakta b\u0131rakt\u0131lar. De ki: \"Allah'\u0131n Kat\u0131nda bulunan, e\u011flenceden ve ticaretten daha hay\u0131rl\u0131d\u0131r. Allah, r\u0131z\u0131k verenlerin en hay\u0131rl\u0131s\u0131d\u0131r.\""}]